    \ import serve\n\n        path('<path:path>', serve, {'document_root': '/path/to/my/files/'})\n\
    \n    in your URLconf. You must provide the ``document_root`` param. You may\n\
    \    also set ``show_indexes`` to ``True`` if you'd like to serve a basic index\n\
    \    of the directory.  This index view will use the template hardcoded below,\n\
    \    but if you'd like to override it, you can create a template called\n    ``static/directory_index.html``.\n\
    \    "
  is_api: false
  is_async: false
  is_rest: false
  methods:
  - GET
  name: ''
  namespace: ''
  parameters:
  - in: path
    name: path
